OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain, occasionally heavy
OL,8,Fat first. Further rain the in the east
OL,9,Fovernight, drier and clearer spells
OL,10,Fwill develop in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FDry for many with bright
OL,13,Fspells but a few showers possible.
OL,14,FThese may be heavy at times.More
OL,15,Ffrequent showers spread into the west
OL,16,Fin the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
